$\square$ Enhance $T$ cell activation by promoting the accumulation of APC at site of exposure
$\square$ Increases expression of co stimulant molecules cytokines, HLA peptide complexes on the APC
$\square$ Slowed release of the Ag for sustained immune stimulation(depot effect)
